《'''母亲节'''》（{{lang-en|''Mother's Day''}}）又名《'''淘气小兵兵母亲节特别节目'''》（''{{lang|en|Rugrats Mother's Day Special}}''<ref name="Lenburg-2006">{{cite book | last = Lenburg | first = Jeff | title = Who's Who in Animated Cartoons: An International Guide to Film & Television's Award-winning and Legendary Animators | year = 2006 | publisher = Hal Leonard Corporation | location = Milwaukee | isbn = 978-1-55783-671-7 | ref = harv | url = https://archive.org/details/whoswhoinanimate0000lenb | accessdate = 2020-08-01 | page = 54}}</ref>）和《'''淘气小兵兵的母亲节'''》（''{{lang|en|Rugrats Mother's Day}}''）<ref name="Name2">{{cite web | url = http://www.nick.com/videos/clip/mothers-day-clip.html | title = Rugrats: 'Rugrats Mother's Day' | publisher = [[尼克儿童频道|Nickelodeon]] | archivedate = 2015-03-10 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150310203419/http://www.nick.com/videos/clip/mothers-day-clip.html}}</ref>，是[[尼克儿童频道|尼克儿童频道]][[動畫劇集|动画电视剧]]《[[淘气小兵兵|淘气小兵兵]]》的[[母亲节|母亲节]][[电视特别节目|特别节目]]，也是第四季的第二集和全剧第67集。节目由乔恩·库克西、阿里·玛丽·马西森、{{lang|en|J}}·大卫·斯提姆、戴维·{{lang|en|N}}·韦斯、苏珊·胡德和埃德·雷斯托共同编剧，诺顿·维尔吉恩与托尼·维安执导，讲述汤米、查基、菲尔和里尔四个孩子想要为完全由爸爸查斯养大的查基找新妈，同时讲述各自对妈妈最美好的回忆。剧情发展表明查基的母亲已死于绝症，他和父亲一起翻看妈妈的遗物，里面还有她为儿子写的诗。与此同时，迪迪计划和妈妈明卡度过完美的母亲节，贝蒂帮斯图搞发明，能够帮助许多有需要的母亲。

《淘气小兵兵》主创人[[保罗·杰曼|保罗·杰曼]]曾提出两种剧情发展走向，解释查基母亲的去向，但[[尼克儿童频道|尼克儿童频道]]高管拒绝接受查基父母离婚或母亲去世的设定。《母亲节》播映前，《淘气小兵兵》很少提及查基的妈妈。杰曼的构想后来经修改获批制作母亲节特别节目，但他已于1993年离开剧组，位置由许多新加入的编剧取代，对没能亲自参与节目制作深感遗憾。

《母亲节》于1997年5月6日在美国首播，是尼克儿童频道为《淘气小兵兵》制作的半小时特别节目。除收入1998年发布的{{lang|en|[[家用录像系统|VHS]]}}录像带《淘气小兵兵：疯狂妈妈》外，本集还与第四季其他分集开放[[数字发行|数字下载]]。节目获评论员好评，其中对至亲死亡情节的处理一再得到回顾评审关注。剧中对[[母乳哺育|母乳哺育]]的正面态度，以及对母爱的宽泛理解都颇受赞誉。《母亲节》获[[有线电视卓越奖|有线电视卓越奖]]儿童电视剧或特别节目编剧奖，以及[[人道奖|人道奖]]儿童动画奖提名。尼克儿童频道递交《母亲节》参与[[第49届黄金时段艾美奖|第49届黄金时段艾美奖]]角逐，《淘气小兵兵》随后获[[黄金时段艾美奖最佳动画节目奖|最佳动画节目奖]]提名。

== 剧情 ==
[[母亲节|母亲节]]来临，安吉莉卡·皮克尔斯（{{lang|en|Angelica Pickles}}）用[[通心粉|通心粉]]在头上摆出雕塑，作为送给母亲的节日礼物，并将母亲节的意义告诉汤米（{{lang|en|Tommy}}）、查基（{{lang|en|Chuckie}}）、菲尔（{{lang|en|Phil}}）和里尔（{{lang|en|Lil}}）。查斯·芬斯特（{{lang|en|Chas Finster}}）将儿子查基送到托儿所，然后把装有妻子遗物的盒子送给朋友迪迪·皮克尔斯（{{lang|en|Didi Pickles}}），他自认还没做好同查基谈起妈妈的准备，不想儿子看到盒子里的东西后难过。汤米、菲尔和里尔都想为母亲准备最棒的礼物，查基也在一边帮忙，但却不知该如何庆祝母亲节。三个孩子向查基谈起他们对妈妈最美好的回忆，菲尔和里尔都说，自己第一次笑就是送给母亲最好的礼物。汤米回想还在[[新生儿重症监护室|新生儿重症监护室]]时，妈妈是如何轻柔地抚慰他。几个孩子想要给查基找新妈妈，他们起初想让汤米的狗或里尔给查基当妈，结果自然很不顺利。安吉莉卡表示，只要查基能帮忙完成通米粉雕塑，她就愿意扮作他的妈妈。镜头切换到另一边，迪迪带着妈妈明卡（{{lang|en|Minka}}）去泡[[健身房|温泉]]，贝蒂·德维尔（{{lang|en|Betty DeVille}}）帮斯图·皮克尔斯（{{lang|en|Stu Pickles}}）搞发明，能够帮助许多有需要的母亲。<ref name="Mother3">{{cite episode | title = Mother's Day | series = [[小淘氣_(動畫)|Rugrats]] | author = Writer: Jon Cooksey & Ali Marie Matheson & J. David Stem & David N. Weiss & Susan Hood & Ed Resto. Director: Norton Virgien & Toni Vian. | network = [[尼克儿童频道|Nickelodeon]] | airdate = 1997-05-06 | season = 4}}</ref>

安吉莉卡派查基去采[[蒲公英|蒲公英]]，用来装饰雕塑，但查基遇上蜜蜂，蒲公英都在逃跑时四下飞散。斯图的发明类似真空吸尘器，但功率实在太强，大片草坪都被摧毁。查基意外弄断通心粉，安吉莉卡命令他与汤米、菲尔和里尔一起呆在衣柜里不准出来。汤米等人安慰查基，后者逐渐意识到，父亲又当爹又当妈，表现完全满足好母亲的一切要求。他们打开查斯送给迪迪的盒子，看到里面有[[圆锹|圆锹]]、[[押花|押花]]杂志，以及查基妈妈的照片。在此期间，斯图的发明还在继续吸入泥土，最终在屋内爆炸。明卡不喜欢泡温泉，迪迪很失望，但妈妈告诉她，母亲节这天只想和女儿在一起。查基把妈妈的照片当做母亲节礼物送给爸爸，查斯决定和儿子好好聊一聊，他告诉查基，妈妈在生下他后不久死于绝症，她在医院时曾把对儿子的爱意写进日记。查斯大声朗读妻子为儿子写的诗，镜头闪动，查基仿佛回到自家后院，念着诗歌的就是妈妈，两人一起快乐玩耍。接下来镜头又一次切换，查基告诉朋友们，妈妈无处不在，一直陪在他身边。<ref name="Mother3" />

== 制作 ==
[[File:Kim_Cattrall_2012_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]在本集客串出演梅琳达]]

《母亲节》全长23分46秒，由乔恩·库克西（{{lang|en|Jon Cooksey}}）、阿里·玛丽·马西森（{{lang|en|Ali Marie Matheson}}）、{{lang|en|J}}·大卫·斯提姆（{{lang|en|J. David Stem}}）、戴维·{{lang|en|N}}·韦斯（{{lang|en|David N. Weiss}}）、苏珊·胡德（{{lang|en|Susan Hood}}）和埃德·雷斯托（{{lang|en|Ed Resto}}）共同编剧<ref name="ITunes1">{{cite web | url = https://itunes.apple.com/us/tv-season/rugrats-season-4/id794055092 | title = Rugrats, Season 4 | date = 2014-01-27 | publisher = [[ITunes_Store|iTunes Store]] (US) | archivedate = 2018-11-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181114141949/https://itunes.apple.com/us/tv-season/rugrats-season-4/id794055092 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="StuffAndThings1" />，诺顿·维尔吉恩（{{lang|en|Norton Virgien}}）与托尼·维安（{{lang|en|Toni Vian}}）执导，[[尼克儿童频道动画工作室|尼克儿童频道动画工作室]]（{{lang|en|Nickelodeon Animation Studio}}）旗下的[[克拉斯基丘波动画工作室|克拉斯基丘波动画工作室]]（{{lang|en|Klasky Csupo}}）制作。制作人包括塞拉·尼科尔斯·达菲（{{lang|en|Cella Nichols Duffy}}）、[[嘉柏·丘波|嘉柏·丘波]]（{{lang|en|Gabor Csupo}}）、[[阿琳·克拉斯基|阿琳·克拉斯基]]（{{lang|en|Arlene Klasky}}）、保罗·德迈尔（{{lang|en|Paul De Meyer}}）、斯提姆和韦斯。节目配乐由[[马克·马瑟斯鲍夫|马克·马瑟斯鲍夫]]（{{lang|en|Mark Mothersbaugh}}）和[[鲁比·安德鲁斯|鲁比·安德鲁斯]]（{{lang|en|Ruby Andrews}}）作曲。<ref name="StuffAndThings1">{{cite web | url = https://www.bcdb.com/cartoon/29603-Mothers-Day | title = Mother's Day (1997) Season 4 Episode 67- Rugrats Cartoon Episode Guide | publisher = [[大卡通数据库|The Big Cartoon DataBase]] | archivedate = 2017-03-08 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20170308011236/https://www.bcdb.com/cartoon/29603-Mothers-Day}}</ref>据《淘气小兵兵》主创人保罗·杰曼（{{lang|en|Paul Germain}}）2016年透露，他曾在多年以前向[[尼克儿童频道|尼克儿童频道]]高管提出本集的初步构想，以及查基母亲的动向。她没有在《淘气小兵兵》第一季露面，这样剧组就无需制作全新的动画角色。第二和第三季制作期间，杰曼发现没有这个角色导致的问题渐显突出。同另一位主创人克拉斯基商议后，两人都认为要解决这个问题，要么是让她和查斯离婚，要么就是在电视剧面世前去世。<ref name="EW1">{{cite journal | url = https://ew.com/article/2016/08/10/rugrats-passover-chuckie-mom/ | title = Rugrats creator talks Chuckie's mom, Passover episode | last = Snetiker | first = Marc | date = 2016-08-10 | journal = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | publisher = Meredith Corporation | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191225012845/https://ew.com/article/2016/08/10/rugrats-passover-chuckie-mom/ | archivedate = 2019-12-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

杰曼和克拉斯基起初的计划是让角色离婚，但尼克儿童频道高管拒绝接受，认为不应该让小观众看到这样的情节。角色死亡的路同样走不通，因为这样“太吓人”，“孩子们不想看到这样的内容”。<ref name="EW1" />这些顾虑导致节目组在前几季《淘气小兵兵》中极少提及查基的母亲，最多只是谈到这个人物，但决不会说明她情况如何。剧组甚至在其中一集对此开过玩笑，但自始至终都不能深入发掘<ref name="EW1" />。即便《母亲节》的剧情已经说明查基的母亲因绝症去世，但没有任何角色说过“死”字<ref name="MP1">{{cite web | url = https://moviepilot.com/posts/4032876 | title = '90s Nostalgia: 'Rugrats' And The Tragic Story Of Melinda Finster! | last = Chapman | first = Tom | date = 2016-08-16 | publisher = Moviepilot | archivedate = 2017-03-12 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170312034207/https://moviepilot.com/posts/4032876}}</ref>。《母亲节》播映前，只有三集《淘气小兵兵》曾短暂提及查基的母亲，其中第一季一集<ref name="Mother1">{{cite episode | title = Real or Robots? | series = [[小淘氣_(動畫)|Rugrats]] | author = Writer: Steve Viksen, Joe Ansolabehere, Patric M. Verrone, & Maya Williams. Director: Norton Virgien. | network = [[尼克儿童频道|Nickelodeon]] | airdate = 1991-12-01 | season = 1}}</ref>，第二季两集<ref name="Mother2">{{cite episode | title = Chuckie vs. the Potty | series = [[小淘氣_(動畫)|Rugrats]] | author = Writer: Jon Greenberg & Joe Ansolabehere. Director: Norton Virgien & Steven Dean Moore. | network = [[尼克儿童频道|Nickelodeon]] | airdate = 1992-09-13 | season = 2}}</ref><ref name="MotherFish">{{cite episode | title = My Friend Barney | series = [[小淘氣_(動畫)|Rugrats]] | author = Writer: Craig Bartlett, Peter Gaffney & Paul Germain. Director: Norton Virgien, Jim Duffy & Steve Socki. | network = [[尼克儿童频道|Nickelodeon]] | airdate = 1993-03-14 | season = 2}}</ref>。

杰曼于1993年离开剧组，位置由许多新加入的编剧取代。尼克儿童频道此时已经允许编剧和[[动画师|动画师]]在节目中加入查基母亲去世的情节。<ref name="EW1" />1996年12月7日，《淘气小兵兵》确定制作母亲节特别节目<ref name="Billboard1">{{cite news | archivedate = 2017-03-08 | deadurl = no | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=uAkEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA72&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | title = Nickelodeon Vids Boost Paramount Kids' Line | last = Fitzpatrick | first = Eileen | date = 1996-12-07 | work = [[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20170308004142/https://books.google.com/books?id=uAkEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA72&dq=%22Rugrats%22+%22Mother's+Day%22&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y%23v=onepage&q=%22Rugrats%22%20%22Mother's%20Day%22&f=false}}</ref>。[[金·凱特羅|金·凱特羅]]为查基的妈妈梅琳达·芬斯特（{{lang|en|Melinda Finster}}）配音<ref name="MP1" />。杰曼觉得这集内容“非常感伤”，对没能亲自参与制作颇感遗憾：“我想起以前，他们根本不允许我们这么干，可现在你们就能干了，对此我很遗憾”<ref <ref name="EW1" />。尼克儿童频道动画监视玛丽·哈灵顿（{{lang|en|Mary Harrington}}）非常喜欢《母亲节》，并称赞众编剧和制作人在处理人物死亡情节上的出色表现<ref name="Decider1">{{cite web | url = https://decider.com/2016/06/16/the-oral-history-of-nicktoons-part-iii-rugrats/ | title = The Oral History Of 'Nicktoons', Part III: Exploring The Multigenerational Appeal Of 'Rugrats' | last2 = Klickstein | first2 = Matthew | date = 2016-06-16 | publisher = Decider | last1 = Gaines | first1 = Caseen | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200204043117/https://decider.com/2016/06/16/the-oral-history-of-nicktoons-part-iii-rugrats/ | archivedate = 2020-02-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

== 播映及家用媒体发行 ==
《母亲节》曾以《淘气小兵兵母亲节特别节目》之名宣传<ref name="Lenburg-2006" />，于[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]1997年5月6日晚20点通过尼克儿童频道在美国首播<ref name="StuffAndThings1" /><ref name="LAT1">{{cite news | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1997-05-04-tv-55161-story.html | title = The final 'Family Matters' on ABC; 'Sabrina' the Showtime Teenage witch; Mother's Day 'Rugrats' | last = Margulies | first = Lee | date = 1997-05-04 | newspaper = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | archivedate = 2017-03-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170312032901/http://articles.latimes.com/1997-05-04/news/tv-55161_1_family-matters}}</ref>。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的李·马古利斯（{{lang|en|Lee Margulies}}）认为本集适合四到八岁的儿童观看<ref name="LAT1" />。尼克儿童频道为《淘气小兵兵》拍过多部半小时长的特别节目，除《母亲节》外，另外几集分别是《体验圣诞老人》（''{{lang|en|The Santa Experience}}''，1992年）、《[[淘气小兵兵的逾越节|淘气小兵兵的逾越节]]》（''{{lang|en|A Rugrats Passover}}''，1993和1995年）和《[[淘气小兵兵的光明节|淘气小兵兵的光明节]]》（1996年）。据作家杰夫·伦伯格（{{lang|en|Jeff Lenburg}}）记载，四集特别节目的收视率都很高。<ref name="Lenburg-2006" />

1998年1月4日，《母亲节》通过《淘气小兵兵：疯狂妈妈》（{{lang|en|''Rugrats: Mommy Mania''}}）{{lang|en|[[家用录像系统|VHS]]}}录像带发布<ref name="Atkinson-Shifrin-2007">{{cite book | last1 = Atkinson | first1 = Michael | last2 = Shifrin | first2 = Lauren | title = Flickipedia: Perfect Films for Every Occasion, Holiday, Mood, Ordeal, and Whim | year = 2007 | publisher = Chicago Review Press | location = Chicago | isbn = 978-1-55652-714-2 | ref = harv | url = https://archive.org/details/flickipediaperfe00atki_0 | page = 37 | accessdate = 2020-08-01}}</ref><ref name="BBFC1">{{cite web | url = https://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/rugrats-mommy-mania-mothers-day-video | title = Rugrats – Mommy Mania – Mother's Day | publisher = [[英國電影分級委員會|British Board of Film Classification]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170312031754/http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/rugrats-mommy-mania-mothers-day-video | archivedate = 2017-03-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，之后又在2011年与第四季其他分集一起发行{{lang|en|[[數碼多功能影音光碟|DVD]]}}套装，新闻稿中称《母亲节》是“特别分集”<ref name="DVD1">{{cite web | archivedate = 2017-03-12 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/releases/Rugrats-Season-4/11654 | title = Rugrats – Season 4 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170312033532/http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/releases/Rugrats-Season-4/11654 | date = 2011-09-23 | publisher = TVShowsOnDVD.com}}</ref>。[[DVD谈论|DVD谈论]]（{{lang|en|DVD Talk}}）网站评论员弗朗西斯·里佐三世（{{lang|en|Francis Rizzo III}}）批评2004年[[维亚康姆|维亚康姆]]发行的{{lang|en|DVD}}合集《淘气小兵兵节日庆典》（{{lang|en|''Rugrats Holiday Celebration''}}）第二张光盘内容不足，应该加入《母亲节》<ref name="StuffAndThings1" /><ref name="DVD">{{cite web | publisher = DVD Talk | last =Rizzo | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200720144022/https://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/12132/rugrats-holiday-celebration/ | archivedate = 2020-07-20 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/12132/rugrats-holiday-celebration/ | title = Rugrats Holiday Celebration | date = 2004-11-01 | first = Francis | accessdate = 2020-08-01}}</ref>。2018年2月6日，[[派拉蒙家用娱乐|派拉蒙家用媒体发行公司]]（{{lang|en|Paramount Home Media Distribution}}）也推出《淘气小兵兵：第四季》{{lang|en|DVD}}，《母亲节》同样收录其中<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180508210526/http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/news/Rugrats-Seasons-3-and-4/23836 | url = http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/news/Rugrats-Seasons-3-and-4/23836 | title = Rugrats - 'Season 3' and 'Season 4' DVDs to 'Go Wide' at General Retail | publisher = TVShowsOnDVD.com | archivedate = 2018-05-08 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2018-05-08}}</ref>。此外，{{lang|en|[[ITunes_Store|iTunes Store]]}}和[[亚马逊影片|亚马逊影片]]均提供包括本集在内整个第四季的付费[[数字发行|数字下载]]<ref name="ITunes1" /><ref name="AmazonM">{{cite web | archivedate = 2017-03-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170312033615/https://www.amazon.com/Rugrats-Mothers-Day/dp/B00I3J65EU/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1488935093&sr=8-1&keywords=rugrats+mother%27s+day | deadurl = no | title = Rugrats | url = https://www.amazon.com/Rugrats-Mothers-Day/dp/B00I3J65EU/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1488935093&sr=8-1&keywords=rugrats+mother%27s+day | publisher = [[亚马逊公司|Amazon.com]]}}</ref>，还能通过{{lang|en|[[Hulu|Hulu]]}}[[流媒体|流媒体]][[随选视讯|随选视讯]]网站观看<ref name="Hulu1">{{cite web | accessdate = 2017-01-02 | url = https://www.hulu.com/watch/861619 | title = Rugrats Mother's Day | publisher = [[Hulu|Hulu]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170102165729/https://www.hulu.com/watch/861619 | archivedate = 2017-01-02 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

== 评价 ==
1998年，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》刊登埃里克·施马克（{{lang|en|Eric Schmuckler}}）的评论文章，称《母亲节》是《淘气小兵兵》在“保持阳光明媚，通常还有点冒傻气”的基调同时，又能体现出“凄美”一面的典范之作。在他看来，在处理孩子失去母亲的问题上，查斯与查基的互动对于这个年龄的孩子来说恰到好处。<ref name="NYT1">{{cite news | date = 1998-08-30 | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190414045426/https://www.nytimes.com/1998/08/30/arts/television-in-rugrats-babies-know-best.html | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1998/08/30/arts/television-in-rugrats-babies-know-best.html | title = Television; In 'Rugrats,' Babies Know Best | last = Schmuckler | first = Eric | archivedate = 2019-04-14 | deadurl = no}}</ref>尼克儿童频道递交《母亲节》参与[[第49届黄金时段艾美奖|第49届黄金时段艾美奖]]角逐后<ref name="StuffAndThings1" />，《淘气小兵兵》获[[黄金时段艾美奖最佳动画节目奖|黄金时段艾美奖最佳动画节目奖]]提名，但最终获奖的是《[[辛普森一家|辛普森一家]]》<ref name="Winner1">{{cite web | url = https://www.emmys.com/shows/simpsons | title = The Simpsons | publisher = Academy of Television Arts & Sciences | archivedate = 2020-07-31 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200731090544/https://www.emmys.com/shows/simpsons}}</ref>。《母亲节》还获得1998年人道奖（{{lang|en|Humanitas Prize}}）儿童动画奖提名<ref name="StuffAndThings1" />，最终不敌《[[与路易生活|与路易生活]]》（''{{lang|en|Life with Louie}}''）分集《盲目的爱》（{{lang|en|''Blinded by Love''}}）<ref name="Winner2">{{cite web | archivedate = 2017-04-05 | deadurl = yes | format = PDF | url = http://humanitasprize.info/HUMANITAS-NEWS-90s/1998%20July%20-%20%20HUMANITAS%20spreads%20'Good%20Will'.pdf | title = Humanitas | publisher = Humanitas Prize | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20170405131615/http://humanitasprize.info/HUMANITAS-NEWS-90s/1998%20July%20-%20%20HUMANITAS%20spreads%20'Good%20Will'.pdf}}</ref>。此外，乔恩·库克西、阿里·玛丽·马西森、{{lang|en|J}}·大卫·斯提姆和戴维·{{lang|en|N}}·韦斯因本集获[[有线电视卓越奖|有线电视卓越奖]]（{{lang|en|CableACE Award}}）儿童电视剧或特别节目编剧奖<ref name="VTY1">{{cite journal | title = CableAce Awards | last = Richmond | first = Ray | date = 1997-11-16 | url = https://variety.com/1997/tv/news/cableace-awards-111661098/ | journal = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190608040154/https://variety.com/1997/tv/news/cableace-awards-111661098/ | archivedate = 2019-06-08 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

《淘气小兵兵》的多篇回顾评述特别关注《母亲节》。{{lang|en|Arts.Mic}}（字面意“艺术.话筒”）的菲利普·刘易斯（{{lang|en|Philip Lewis}}）称本集堪称尼克儿童频道涉足严肃主题的典范，剧中对失去至亲情节的处理也是整部动画片中非常令人难忘的瞬间<ref name="Mic1">{{cite web | url = https://www.mic.com/articles/132324/5-times-nickelodeon-cartoons-tackled-real-issues#.3TEqOo2os | title = 5 Times Nickelodeon Cartoons Tackled Real Issues | last = Lewis | first = Philip | date = 2016-01-12 | publisher = Art.Mic | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200101182408/https://www.mic.com/articles/132324/5-times-nickelodeon-cartoons-tackled-real-issues#.3TEqOo2os | archivedate = 2020-01-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。克里斯蒂·安德森（{{lang|en|Kristy Anderson}}）在网上杂志《[[电影剧情|电影剧情]]》（{{lang|en|Moviepilot}}）发文，称查基的背景故事堪称惊喜，因为大多数观众都想不到会在婴儿题材动画片中看到死亡主题内容<ref name="MPSomethingDark">{{cite web | url = https://moviepilot.com/posts/4102801 | title = 10 Animated Characters With Horribly Tragic Backstories | last = Anderson | first = Kristy | date = 2016-10-03 | publisher = Moviepilot | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170312061540/https://moviepilot.com/posts/4102801 | archivedate = 2017-03-12 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。迈克尔·阿特金森（{{lang|en|Michael Atkinson}}）和劳雷尔·希夫林（{{lang|en|Laurel Shifrin}}）的著作《{{lang|en|Flickipedia}}：适合在任何场合、假日、心情、苦难和起意之时观看的完美电影》（{{lang|en|''Flickipedia: Perfect Films for Every Occasion, Holiday, Mood, Ordeal, and Whim''}}）与安德森看法接近，称《母亲节》的情节震撼程度“仿佛卡车撞人”<ref name="Atkinson-Shifrin-2007" />。

《母亲节》在许多评论员评选的《淘气小兵兵》最佳分集或情节榜上有名。安德森将本集列入电视剧第三到五季必看分集，还建议观众“准备纸巾”<ref name="MP2">{{cite web | url = https://moviepilot.com/posts/4026124 | title = 25 Years Of 'Rugrats' 21 Episodes You Need To Watch Part 2: Seasons 3, 4, & 5 | last = Anderson | first = Kristy | date = 2016-08-18 | publisher = Moviepilot | archivedate = 2017-03-12 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170312033350/https://moviepilot.com/posts/4026124}}</ref>。《电影剧情》的丹尼尔·皮尔森（{{lang|en|Daniel Pearson}}）对查基母亲创作并念诵的诗作称颂有加<ref name="MP3">{{cite web | url = https://moviepilot.com/posts/2814884 | title = This Little Known 'Rugrats' Trivia Will Break Your Heart: The Devastatingly Beautiful Poem Left by Chuckie's Mom! | last = Pearson | first = Daniel | date = 2015-03-27 | publisher = Moviepilot | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180102091334/https://moviepilot.com/posts/2814884 | archivedate = 2018-01-02 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>，该杂志的玛拉·穆利金（{{lang|en|Mara Mullikin}}）也将这首诗列入《淘气小兵兵》最感人的八大瞬间<ref name="MP5">{{cite web | url = https://moviepilot.com/posts/3513467 | title = 8 Heartfelt Animated TV Moments | last = Mullikin | first = Mara | date = 2015-10-02 | publisher = Moviepilot | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170312032554/https://moviepilot.com/posts/3513467 | archivedate = 2017-03-12 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[A+_(网站)|A+]]}}网站刊登维克多·贝格曼（{{lang|en|Victor Beigelman}}）的文章，将《母亲节》选入七大母亲节主题电视剧分集，称赞剧中的“浓重乡思”<ref name="APlus1">{{cite web | url = http://aplus.com/a/7-mothers-day-tv-episodes?no_monetization=true | title = 7 Mother's Day-Themed TV Episodes To Make You Appreciate Your Mom Even More | last = Beigelman | first = Victor | date = 2016-05-04 | publisher = A Plus | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170312034732/http://aplus.com/a/7-mothers-day-tv-episodes?no_monetization=true | archivedate = 2017-03-12 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

部分文章从其他角度评述《母亲节》。2016年，《[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]》的卡罗琳·博洛尼亚（{{lang|en|Caroline Bologna}}）赞扬剧中正面描绘[[母乳哺育|母乳哺育]]并向所有年龄段的观众正名。博洛尼亚指出，当代儿童电视节目大多不会出现母乳哺育的画面，但《母亲节》打破常规、影响积极，用事实证明“该主题非常适合20年前的儿童节目”。<ref name="HP1">{{cite news | accessdate = 2019-12-27 | url = https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/remember-when-rugrats-normalized-breastfeeding_us_57befba7e4b04193420db778 | title = Remember When 'Rugrats' Normalized Breastfeeding? | last = Bologna | first = Caroline | date = 2016-08-25 | newspaper = [[赫芬顿邮报|The Huffington Post]] | publisher = [[美国在线|AOL]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191227004140/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/remember-when-rugrats-normalized-breastfeeding_n_57befba7e4b04193420db778 | archivedate = 2019-12-27 | deadurl = no}}</ref>普里西拉·布洛森（{{lang|en|Priscilla Blossom}}）在母爱网站{{lang|en|Romper.com}}发文，称赞剧中涉及[[生殖健康|生殖健康]]议题的内容，以及汤米早产后呆在新生儿重症监护室的情节<ref name="Romper1">{{cite web | url = https://www.romper.com/p/13-reasons-rugrats-was-the-most-feminist-socially-conscious-cartoon-ever-1665 | title = 13 Reasons 'Rugrats' Was The Most Feminist, Socially Conscious Cartoon Ever | last = Bloom | first = Priscilla | date = 2015-11-24 | publisher = Romper.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190516222638/https://www.romper.com/p/13-reasons-rugrats-was-the-most-feminist-socially-conscious-cartoon-ever-1665 | archivedate = 2019-05-16 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。2013年，学者[[杰克·德雷舍|杰克·德雷舍]]（{{lang|en|Jack Drescher}}）、黛博拉·格雷泽（{{lang|en|Deborah F. Glazer}}）、李·克里斯皮（{{lang|en|Lee Crespi}}）和大卫·施瓦兹（{{lang|en|David Schwartz}}）刊发论文《什么叫母亲？同性恋的育儿观》（{{lang|en|''What Is a Mother? Gay and Lesbian Perspectives on Parenting''），利用[[精神分析学|精神分析学家]][[唐纳德·威尼科特|唐纳德·威尼科特]]的幼儿理论全面分析《母亲节》。文中指出，查基理解父亲已经尽到母亲职责的一刻体现出“[[后现代主义|后现代主义]]洞察力”，将母爱范围提升到新的高度。<ref name="Drescher-Glazer-Crespi-Schwartz-2013">{{cite book | last1 = Drescher | first1 = Jack | last2 = Glazer | first2 = Deborah F. | last3 = Crespi | first3 = Lee | last4 = Schwartz | first4 = David | chapter = What Is a Mother? Gay and Lesbian Perspectives on Parenting | editor-last = Brown | editor-first = Sheila F. | title = What Do Mothers Want?: Developmental Perspectives, Clinical Challenges | year = 2013 | publisher = Routledge | location = Hillsdale | isbn = 978-0-88163-400-6 | ref = harv | page = 96}}</ref>

